    Oshi

    Oshi is a blockchain-enabled open anime platform that transforms how fans engage with and support their favorite anime. Through Oshi, fans directly support anime projects they’re passionate about, receiving exclusive benefits and sharing in their global growth and commercial success. The platform’s IP licensing infrastructure enables IP owners to maintain control of their work while connecting with dedicated global partners, ensuring anime properties can reach their full potential worldwide.
